## Objectives

| Objective | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| Understand Traffic Descriptors & Profiles | Identify and explain the parameters used to describe and classify data traffic. |
| Understand Congestion Control Categories | Differentiate between open-loop and closed-loop congestion control approaches. |
